The paper presents a novel embedding method based on graph neural networks, which is a popular topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method deals with graph isomorphism and preserves the metric structure of the graph domain, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the computational cost of the method, which is relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
